Live Music and Events
Have Fun in Our Irish Restaurant
Listen to live music and experience fun events at Molly Malone’s Irish Pub. Our Irish restaurant in Tampa, FL, welcomes regulars and walk-in customers. Our newly renovated pub features stylish décor, and our outdoor deck is great for groups and families with kids. We also have excellent waiter service as well as take-out service. Check out our list of events to get an idea of what you can expect when you visit our restaurant.

Live Sports at Molly’s
Here at Molly Malone’s Irish Pub, we love sports, and we proudly show the NHL Lightning, NFL Buccaneers, Premiere League Soccer, European Cup, World Cup Soccer, Rugby, and more!
